{"tid":1047463,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島去屋久島搭咩船好","createTime":"2019-03-05T03:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T16:23:32.000Z","uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a4eb9a23f2f80433b61e59abc0e72dc05bf2b1e3","tid":1047463,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"有沒巴打試過通宵船hibiscus?<br />\n猶豫梗要坐高速船定通宵<br />\n中價慢船𣎴考慮，去到太晏<br />\n當日就幾乎沒時間起行<br />\n<br />\n通宵船價錢和高速船真的差太多<br />\n而且時間會仲夾啲<br />\n落船食完早餐出發剛剛好有一整日<br />\n但很擔心會唔會不好休息<br />\n或太飄會暈船<br />\n到埗剩半條人命沒法行山就得不償失<br />\nGoogle左陣都唔見有人講搭呢班船"},{"pid":"290bf1fe71ffcfd0ee86f1fff0b502a464163455","tid":1047463,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"貨櫃船改幾個位用嚟載客<br />\n設備喺點唔駛多講<br />\n<br />\n仲有行嘅係外海所以&hellip;明嘅就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd24b57a06ce9834b82376904559483ee4b4431","tid":1047463,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"你問得出呢個問題就坐高速船啦<br />\n<br />\n利申: 極少暈船浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b32633c28015f0cf252ccc48ae57f5bc54d8b13","tid":1047463,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"290bf1fe71ffcfd0ee86f1fff0b502a464163455","tid":1047463,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"貨櫃船改幾個位用嚟載客<br />\n設備喺點唔駛多講<br />\n<br />\n仲有行嘅係外海所以&hellip;明嘅就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"就咁睇我ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過外海=大浪=<img